Subject: [PATCH v5 05/26] media: v4l: Support line-based metadata capture
Date:   Wed, 27 Sep 2023 19:31:51 +0300
Message-Id: <20230927163212.402025-6-sakari.ailus@linux.intel.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.39.2
In-Reply-To: <20230927163212.402025-1-sakari.ailus@linux.intel.com>
